metadata.title: Synthetic Node Coordinate Dataset
metadata.description: Complete 9x9 grid mapping with 12 known nodes and 69 synthetic coordinates
metadata.methodology: Geometric interpolation based on distance from center (5,5), nearest node influence, and axis blending

known_nodes.name: Identity Inner
known_nodes.subtitle: Instinct
known_nodes.shedding: Recognize compromise as your nature. Incorporating others, balancing opposites and respecting duality is appreciated. However, this measured approach must be released from the focus of your life.
known_nodes.integrating: Address precarious, stagnant energy. In seeking approval, you sacrifice trust in your own instincts. Integrate your complementary desire to find ease in individuality.
known_nodes.grounding: Honor your impulses. Embrace unwavering selfhood. Go on solo adventures. Grounding this energy means developing a 'me' focus, taking risks with confidence.

known_nodes.name: Experience Inner
known_nodes.subtitle: Seen
known_nodes.shedding: Recognize intensity as your nature. Transformation, energy contracts, emotional complexity are appreciated. However, this deep, entangled approach must be released from the focus of your life.
known_nodes.integrating: Address mistrusting, chaos-prone energy. Involving in power dynamics, protecting against the shadow side of situations, you sacrifice ease and calm. Integrate your complementary desire for stable self-reliance.
known_nodes.grounding: Center your value. Settle into structure. Be in nature. Please your senses. Form boundaries to preserve your peace. Draw power from serenity and reliable experiences.

known_nodes.name: Language Inner
known_nodes.subtitle: Ideas
known_nodes.shedding: Recognize philosophy and adventure as your nature. Seeing the bigger picture is appreciated. However, this profound approach must be released from the focus of your life.
known_nodes.integrating: Address unapproachable energy. Exalting your virtues or exaggerated personal freedom comes at the sacrifice of simple curiosity. Integrate a complementary desire to converse without bias.
known_nodes.grounding: Let others inform you. Play with ideas. Detach from staunch perspectives. Grounding this energy means embracing the temporary nature of a zeitgeist.

known_nodes.name: Domain Inner
known_nodes.subtitle: Source
known_nodes.shedding: Recognize material ambition as your nature. Climbing to reach tangible goals is appreciated. However, this stoic approach must be released from the focus of your life.
known_nodes.integrating: Address melancholic energy. Pursuing established status for yourself or others, you sacrifice nurturing internal emotions and external connections. Integrate a complementary need for vulnerability, deep personal experiences.
known_nodes.grounding: Tend to your feelings. Create rituals. Withdraw from public eyes. Nurture the hearts of others, helping you pour into yourself.

known_nodes.name: Purpose Inner
known_nodes.subtitle: Heart
known_nodes.shedding: Recognize logic as your nature. Progressive, humanitarian thinking is appreciated. However, this intellectual approach must be released from the focus of your life.
known_nodes.integrating: Address detached, group-oriented energy. Focusing on collective needs or social advocacy, you sacrifice the inner child desire for play. Integrate your complementary desire for creative expression.
known_nodes.grounding: Lead with your heart. Integrate drama. Initiate romance. Take center stage and inspire others. Love and generosity will help you channel your innate altruism into purposeful achievements.

known_nodes.name: Order Inner

known_nodes.integrating: Address self-undoing energy. Empathizing with those around you, you sacrifice your emotional health and psychic wellbeing. Integrate a complementary desire to say no.
known_nodes.grounding: Create healthy structure and routine. Get organized. Maintain physical and energetic tidiness. Make detail-oriented plans.

known_nodes.name: Identity Outer

known_nodes.shedding: Recognize individuating as your nature. Drive, discovery and following your instincts is appreciated. However, this youthful just-do-it approach must be released from the focus of your life.
known_nodes.integrating: Address impulsive, self-focused energy. Blazing your path, you sacrifice the ability to integrate complementary people or perspectives. Integrate your desire to experience ease in partnership.
known_nodes.grounding: Share, hold space for others. Consider their needs and experience. See both sides of an argument before making decisions.

known_nodes.name: Experience Outer

known_nodes.integrating: Address controlling, rigid energy. Holding on to situations or a comfort zone, you sacrifice deep personal growth opportunities. Integrate a complementary desire to purge, exchange and experience transformation.
known_nodes.grounding: Go deep and transmute. Discard stale limitations. Release unnecessary boundaries. The more you let go, the more you step into new life.
